---

<section id="browser-first" class="landing-section">
  <div class="landing-shell">
    <div class="browser-card" data-reveal>
      <div class="browser-copy">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Sin instalación</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Sin descargar ninguna app</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">
          Parmelia corre desde el navegador, por lo que no necesitas descargar nada.
        </p>

        <svg class="bridge-cross" viewBox="0 0 260 170" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <polygon points="52,70 88,88 52,106 16,88" fill="#DEA6BC" />
          <polygon points="208,70 244,88 208,106 172,88" fill="#A7D4DE" />
          <path class="bridge-arc" d="M 72,78 Q 130,24 188,78" fill="none" stroke="#F5F5F3" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <path class="bridge-arc bridge-arc-delay" d="M 72,98 Q 130,150 188,98" fill="none" stroke="#F5F5F3" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="phone-shot" data-float>
        <img src="/app.png" alt="Captura de Parmelia en móvil" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
